# Product Quality

- Every page must have one clear primary action:
  Homepage → Apply for Your Merchant Account
  Pricing → Choose Your Plan
  Cards → Get Your Charm Card
  Contact → Send Message

- All async operations must include loading states.
- All error states must provide an explanation and a next step.
- Button labels must describe actions. Avoid: "Submit", "Continue",
  "Click here". Use descriptive actions instead.
- One primary CTA per page — no competing actions.
